OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FThe war in Iran is causing jet fuel
OL,7,Fprices to soar, pushing up the cost of
OL,8,Fflights and leading to some
OL,9,Fholidaymakers rethinking where to
OL,10,Ftravel this year.
OL,12,FHowever, Brits are still opting for
OL,13,Fmore long-haul destinations despite
OL,14,Fthe price increases.
OL,16,FAccording to Mark Duguid at the travel
OL,17,Fagents Kuoni, the Caribbean,
OL,18,FMauritius, North America, and, closer
OL,19,Fto home, the Western Mediterranean,
OL,20,Fare top of the list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FDuguid told ITV News that enquiries
OL,7,Ffor the Caribbean are up 50%. However,
OL,8,Fas for prices of flights, a seat in
OL,9,Feconomy would set you back an extra
OL,10,F#1,000 per person.
OL,12,FDuguid said: "Flight prices are
OL,13,Fstarting to level out.
OL,15,F"We saw an immediate reaction,
OL,16,Fparticularly over Easter, where the
OL,17,Fcapacity was limited, and there was a
OL,18,Fsurge of demand for those sorts of
OL,19,Fplaces."
OL,26,@tD@NOUwD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
