OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FHowever, since the Iran conflict,
OL,7,Fmarkets show jet fuel prices have
OL,8,Fsharply increased, rising from $0.60
OL,9,Fto $1.10 per litre in two weeks.
OL,11,FITV News has found that several
OL,12,Fairlines have already introduced fuel
OL,13,Fsurcharges.
OL,15,FVirgin Atlantic have recently
OL,16,Fincreased its carrier-imposed
OL,17,Fsurcharges due to external factors,
OL,18,Fsuch as oil prices and insurance
OL,19,Fimpacting operating costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
