FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FA Virgin Atlantic spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our focus is always on our customers
OL,8,Fand giving them the best service and
OL,9,Fexperience at a competitive price.
OL,11,F"As with all airlines, we operate a
OL,12,Fdynamic pricing system based on supply
OL,13,Fand demand which means prices vary."
OL,15,FKLM Royal Dutch Airlines has also
OL,16,Fincreased its economy return tickets
OL,17,Fby E10 (#8.60) for short and medium-
OL,18,Fhaul flights since March 16.
OL,20,FMeanwhile, long-haul fares have gone
OL,21,Fup by E50 (#43) from March 11.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@dO]yD@DOk}D@GOk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
