CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FA KLM spokesperson has said: "Despite
OL,7,Fchanging ticket prices due to
OL,8,Fincreased demand and the fuel
OL,9,Fsurcharge, we have not seen a decline
OL,10,Fin the number of bookings so far."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, AirAsia has taken a similar
OL,13,Fapproach, introducing fuel surcharges
OL,14,Fin response to rising costs.
OL,26,@nD@^OUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
