OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FFarouk Kamal, Deputy Group CEO of
OL,7,FAirAsia X said: "AirAsia X (AAX) has
OL,8,Frecently made adjustments to fare and
OL,9,Ffuel surcharges across its network,
OL,10,Ffollowing the recent increase in
OL,11,Fglobal jet fuel prices - a measure the
OL,12,Fairline assures is temporary.
OL,14,F"AAX will dynamically monitor market
OL,15,Fconditions and react proactively as
OL,16,Fand when needed.
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,F"AAX maintains that the adjustment to
OL,7,Fthe fuel surcharges was necessary, and
OL,8,Fwill allow the airline to maintain
OL,9,Foperational reliability whilst
OL,10,Fsustaining its network connectivity
OL,11,Facross the region."
OL,13,FAt the same time, flights are being
OL,14,Frerouted to avoid the Middle East,
OL,15,Fincreasing the journey times and
OL,16,Fadding to fuel costs.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
