CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FFlight Centre Travel Agent Joe Bevis
OL,7,Fsaid: "Some of these airlines have
OL,8,Fpaid for these fuel prices in advance,
OL,9,Fso some airlines will be able to keep
OL,10,Fprices at the same level for a longer
OL,11,Fperiod of time.
OL,13,F"Other airlines may not have that
OL,14,Fpolicy and will be impacted by fuel
OL,15,Fprices a bit quicker."
OL,17,FTravel experts say that could soon
OL,18,Ffeed through into higher prices for
OL,19,Fholidaymakers.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
