FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773936670
OL,3,CJet fuel prices surge: What does it
OL,4,Cmean for your summer holiday?
OL,6,FZoe Harris from OnTheBeach added: "If
OL,7,Fthis pattern continues, we would
OL,8,Fexpect prices to the west med, so
OL,9,FSpain, Canaries etc, to start creeping
OL,10,Fup.
OL,12,F"So if you're thinking about those
OL,13,Fareas, now is the time to get
OL,14,Fcommitted while the prices are still
OL,15,Fat the levels they are."
OL,17,FFor now, travellers are being urged to
OL,18,Fbook sooner rather than later as
OL,19,Fairlines adjust to rising fuel costs.
OL,26,@nD@cOUtD@AOUwD@XO]
